headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Ralph Lauren (RL) After Its Strong Multi Year Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether Ralph Lauren shares still offer value after a strong run, this article will walk through what the current price might be implying. The stock last closed at US$352.99, with returns of 39.2% over 1 year and 191.5% over 3 years. The past month and year to date show small declines of 1.1% and 2.6%, and the 7 day return shows a 4.5% decline.
